reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Powers any us voltage wired video doorbell
reviews.reviewText: Video doorbells are a great home security device, but not everyone has the proper wiring and transformer at their house. Or they may want to put an extra doorbell where one doesn't currently exist.This device solves those problems. Simply attach the two leads to the two screws on the back of the doorbell, and plug in the adapter. Boom, a video doorbell wherever you have a normal plug outlet!
